user.name: INTERSTATE
user.bio: Interstate is composed of a team of industry veterans who have had the privilege of working with the best artists in the industry and within the most renowned facilities in the world. We were born out of the desire to readapt the traditional production company model to today’s evolving creative challenges. Simultaneously collaborative and individual in our directorial vision, our core values are simple: creative integrity, visual excellence and high artistic value.
user.short_bio: Founded in 2015 by Executive Producer Danny Rosenbloom and Creative Director Yann Mabille, INTERSTATE is a new and spirited inter-disciplinary director’s group.
